high_descs: Walk right and face the sink.
Grab the spoon next to the potted plant.
Turn around and walk right to face the table.
Place the spoon in the skillet.
Grab the skillet from the table.
Turn right and face the sink again.
Place the skillet in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the skillet with the spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right then walk straight then turn right facing the counter beside the sink
Pick up the spoon on the counter
Turn to your left walk straight then turn right facing the table
Put the spoon on the pan at the table
Pick up the pan with spoon on the table
Turn to your right then walk straight head to the sink
Put the pan with spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with spoon in the sink

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Place the spoon on the table.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a spoon on the table and a pan in the sink.
